msg":"新版會唔會可以上網log in後就有個紅色button，用mouse click落去就可以射核彈？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"UEFI介面 一鍵發射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ac4660d26119da7fbc6ec28d02b4bfc1babc7a","tid":1666871,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da25e9f52bf7d63b9c1cdf3043976b733a24241f","tid":1666871,"uid":22822,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"7b86c0ae677d0b5c2b4fd75391ce17237ea6e778","tid":1666871,"uid":112416,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:23:02.000Z","msg":"新版會唔會可以上網log in後就有個紅色button，用mouse click落去就可以射核彈？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"Hey siri..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:32:55.000Z","msg":"help me to shoot the KaBOOM"},{"pid":"3abf4ff7ebcd9a1e7fd0755ebf066570c6268d63","tid":1666871,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:41:14.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"6ffa96b34bb978e728be0a0d5813a8ed09163345","tid":1666871,"uid":125385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"好係有D system 仲用緊Window 2003<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65979ab7632eca451578b9db0c659ded7322eb0b","tid":1666871,"uid":1123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ffa96b34bb978e728be0a0d5813a8ed09163345","tid":1666871,"uid":125385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"好係有D system 仲用緊Window 2003<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"2003 咁新<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b5c7e2081dc3465431bcd0938fd4d6e53d8e51","tid":1666871,"uid":69013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6197aae9efba536cb122e705bf351dce9af5e8c4","tid":1666871,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:00:10.000Z","msg":"MOV @Rn, #immediate<br />\nMOV A, direct<br />\nADD A, @Ri<br />\nAssembly codes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdf973ec23b7960f54cb7dbedf58d44f244cae5","tid":1666871,"uid":279356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:36:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4rWyof9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4rWyof9.gif&h=0c250780&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05f276f8187f2e7aeb35893b24fd0dafc1ce3be7","tid":1666871,"uid":49699,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"IBM = LENOVO = 支那野<br />\n美國核武已經掌握左係支那手中"},{"pid":"eb487027140ebb91d1f226c090cac88159d01901","tid":1666871,"uid":73818,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"05f276f8187f2e7aeb35893b24fd0dafc1ce3be7","tid":1666871,"uid":49699,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T01:26:42.000Z","msg":"IBM = LENOVO = 支那野<br />\n美國核武已經掌握左係支那手中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"Lenovo 好似只喺買咗ibm 個人電腦果part <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f86e2e802ffd499506c77ea6b1aa79ebdf0bb4","tid":1666871,"uid":36162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15b5c7e2081dc3465431bcd0938fd4d6e53d8e51","tid":1666871,"uid":69013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:39:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2KSahAoOLdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2KSahAoOLdU&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=fac8050f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2KSahAoOLdU</a><br />\n<br />\nApollo Guidance Computer 係咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae99110ba3fa72b9953f86f52f046c846a8e798c","tid":1666871,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T09:50:41.000Z","msg":"no way to hack in"},{"pid":"4557132b9ff1746d537bb27dc249e9cdc4dc9de7","tid":1666871,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"想知俄羅斯、中國用乜？"},{"pid":"10366adc1737422032675cb028903ba72d59557e","tid":1666871,"uid":21819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T06:04:55.000Z","msg":"你不能破解沒有 IP 地址的東西。這是一個非常獨特的系統，它既舊又非常好。<br />\n<br />\n呢個真呀 煩少樣"}]}